SUMMARY:The Bike Garage Open Hours: Woodland Location
DESCRIPTION:Woodland location: 1st and Hays streets at Douglass Middle School\n\n\n\n\n\nFREE Bike Repair \n\n\nCome to the Bike Garage\, where our volunteer mechanics will repair your bike. We accept cash\, Venmo\, and Paypal donations. \nInterested in becoming a volunteer bike mechanic? No experience is necessary. \n\n\nCONTACT US TO VOLUNTEER \n\n\nQuality Used Bikes for SaleLowest prices on the best used bikes.Our inventory changes every day!   \n\n\nHybrid bikes\, town bikes\, vintage bikes\, road bikes\, mountain bikes\, kids’ bikes\, and more.  \nVisit the Bike Garage in Davis or Woodland to check out our inventory. \n 
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/the-bike-garage-open-hours-woodland-location-3/2026-04-11/
LOCATION:Bike Garage Woodland\, 1st & Hayes
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/unnamed.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="The Bike Campaign":MAILTO:funmaria@sbcglobal.net
END:VEVENT
