SUMMARY:Davis Makerspace Repair Cafe
DESCRIPTION:Take a shot at giving new life to your broken items. Tools and volunteers will be on hand to help. \n  \nDavis Makerspace and Davis Yololab are hosting a Repair Café on Saturday April 11th\, 2026 in the Blanchard Room at the Mary L. Stephens Davis Branch of the Yolo County Library from 11am to 1pm. \n  \nInstead of buying the same gadgets again and again\, how about having the the ‘good one’ that’s been gathering dust in the corner repaired? At repair cafes\, volunteers stand by to repair broken items brought in by the community.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/davis-makerspace-repair-cafe/
LOCATION:Mary L. Stephens Davis Branch Library Blanchard Room\, 315 E 14th St\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community
END:VEVENT
